data.description: Impressive and desirable 8 bedroom home on 33 acres (3 parcels) of land, offering opportunity for keeping cows, horses, and maintaining healthy garden. there is the opportunity for short term and long term rental as basement apartment is currently rented. Spacious shop (53x84) with caged workshop (24x24) and loft above (36x54)two horse stalls Back feild is fenced and ready for your animals well produces about 60 gallons per minute in its own secluded well house.Additional ADU that needs finishing for more rental dollars.Sellers have raised 14 kids in home and are relocating to GA and request 30 days after close to move. additional contiguous parcels see listings x xx & xxx
